{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/Datebase/mariaDB","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"acdc398f-dd7d-5521-8ead-e3e1f0da386d","html":"<p>mysql 삭제하기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo rm <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>rf <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>usr<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>local<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>var<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>mysql\nsudo rm <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>rf <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>usr<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>local<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token builtin\">bin</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>mysql<span class=\"token operator\">*</span>\nsudo rm <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>rf <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>usr<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>local<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Cellar<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>mysql</code></pre></div>\n<p>mariaDB 설치하기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">brew install mariadb</code></pre></div>\n<p>mariaDB 서버 키기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">mysql<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>server start</code></pre></div>\n<p>mariaDB에 접속하기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">mysql <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token keyword\">u</span> root</code></pre></div>\n<p>만약 Access denied 에러가 발생한다면</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">ERROR <span class=\"token number\">1698</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">28000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Access denied <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> user ‘root’@‘localhost’</code></pre></div>\n<p>아래 방법대로 하기!!</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo mysql <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token keyword\">u</span> root <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>컴퓨터 비밀번호 입력해서 접속한 다음\nuse mysql<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nselect <span class=\"token function\">password</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>‘설정할 비밀번호‘<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nalter user’root’@‘localhost’ identified by ‘비밀번호’<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/Datebase/mariaDB","tagSlugs":["/tag/maria-db/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-05-25","description":"mac에서 mysql 삭제 후 mariaDB 설치하기","tags":["mariaDB"],"title":"mysql 삭제 후 mariaDB 설치하기","socialImage":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/Datebase/mariaDB"}}}